Spell:  Eating of the dead [9129]

Usage:  USE 9129 <dead noble>

Required aura:  3
Required item:  ratspider venom
Time to cast:   seven days

The mage executes a complex ritual where the ratspider venom is
ingested and the brains of the dead noble are consumed.  The mage
will acquire skills and any secret knowledge from the noble's
memories.

This ritual poses great danger to the mage.  The toxic venom of the
ratspider may cause insanity or death.  Furthermore, civilized men
look with horror on this practice, and will go to great lengths to
seek out and kill necromancers who make use of it.

