Spell:  Exhume dead bodies [9130]

Usage:  USE 9130

Required aura:  none
Required item:  none
Time to cast:   seven days

The necromancer steals out under cover of darkness to raid fresh graves
in search of bodies.  A dead body is a deceased peasant, worker, sailor
or soldier.  If any corpses are found, they will be added to the
necromancer's inventory.

Citizens usually become enraged when the graves of their family
or neighbors are violated.  As such, this order carries some risk
of physical harm.

